RANKERS LIFE COMPANY OF DES MOINES, IOWA, appellant, v. Margaret C. ALVAREZ, Individually and as Independent Executrix of the Estate of John A. Alvarez, Deceased, Appellee. No. 10392. Circuit Court of Appeals, Fifth Circuit. Nov. 27, 1942. Rehearing Denied Feh. 4, 1943. Frank G. Dyer, of Houston, Tex., for appellant. Larry W. Morris, of Houston, Tex., for appellee.

Before HOLMES and McCORD, Circuit Judges, and STRUM, District Judge.

PER CURIAM.

The judgment appealed from in this case is affirmed.
